
## MQTT Topics
- `waterfront/{location}/{code}/debug`: Health telemetry
- `waterfront/{location}/{code}/alert`: Fatal errors
- `waterfront/machine/{code}/status`: Machine status
- `waterfront/slots/{id}/status`: Slot status
- `waterfront/locations/{code}/depositRelease`: Deposit release
- `waterfront/locations/{code}/returnConfirm`: Return confirmation

## Power Management
- Monitors battery and solar voltage every 60 seconds
- Enters deep sleep if battery < threshold or solar < min
- LTE modem powered down if WiFi connected and idle > 5 min
- LTE modem powered down if solar voltage low

## Provisioning
- BLE GATT service for WiFi credentials
- SoftAP web server as fallback
- Stores credentials in NVS

## OTA Updates
- ArduinoOTA with password protection
- Saves current FW version to NVS before update
- Publishes progress and errors to MQTT
- Clears saved version on success

## Error Handling
- Fatal errors logged and published to MQTT
- ESP restart on fatal errors
- Watchdog on all tasks (12s timeout)

## Testing
- Unit tests with Catch2 for core functions
- Mocks for hardware and network dependencies
- Coverage for config, MQTT, deposit, sensor, LTE, error handling

## Security
- TLS with CA and optional client certs
- MQTT authentication
- OTA password protection
- NVS for sensitive data

## Performance
- Low power consumption with deep sleep
- Efficient MQTT reconnection
- Minimal heap usage

